{
  "texts": [
    "Still, it has difficulty identifying issues related to deeper structural and pragmatic aspects like human experts, and it also sometimes fabricates errors when the input is correct [13].However, although LLMs' assistance would be helpful for EFL learners to improve their writing skills, whether they can enhance student's writing motivation remains uncertain.",
    "The participants in Song and Song's study reflected that the interaction with ChatGPT made them more confident and engaged during the writing process.",
    "[11] Similarly, through Guo and Li's research on Chinese undergraduate students, creating and using personalized retrieval augmented generation (RAG) chatbots enables augmentative writing to not only address their problems, but also increase their confidence and motivate them to improve [14].",
    "Conversely, a study conducted on Hong Kong Secondary school students showed that teaching and training them to write with ChatGPT enhanced learning motivation insignificantly, and this increase might be attributed to the \"novelty effect\".",
    "In addition, crafting appropriate prompts for ChatGPT has the risk of increasing students' cognitive load, which could overwhelm them [15].All in all, there are plenty of articles about enhancing EFL learners' writing skills with LLMs as assistive or correction tools, and they show consistently positive results."
  ]
}